item.title: My router
item.dc:creator: @93dcthugs93 93dcthugs93
item.description:
@93dcthugs93 wrote:

On the back of your router there should be the words ‘Reset’ etched into the plastic. Right under that is a little rubber button in a hole, take a knife or something and poke the button, hold it for 10 seconds.

Everything will be reset.
